name: Nutricity.com
overview:
Nutricity.com is a pure online retailer focused on providing the largest selection of health products in one place. With over Thirty thousand products and growing we offer one of the largest online health catalogs. The site aggregates brands large and small to offer the most comprehensive selection available online.

Nutricity.com was founded in 2006 when a strategic partnership was formed with a local health store retailer. Nutricity.com started marketing the health stores products online and reached one million dollars in sales the first fiscal year of operation, 2007. Nutricity.com has enjoyed sustained double digit growth every quarter since.

Nutricity.com now services tens of thousands visitors daily via its world-class website and other third party sites. As of August 2009, orders began shipping out of our new state-of-the-art distribution center in Scottsdale, Arizona.

In 2011, Nutricity ranked 831 on the INC 5000 list of fastest growing privately owned companies. Nutricity’s products have also been featured in Martha Stewart Wedding and Lucky magazine. Nutricity currently fills around 35,000 customer orders per month and has shipped over half a million orders since 2007.
